ds for Television]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 2006\n| Asian Television Awards\n| Best Drama Series\n| ''Magpakailanman'' (\"Kalbaryo ng Isang Ina: Patricia Dongallo Story\")\n| {{Included|Highly Commended}}\n!\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | [[20th PMPC Star Awards for Television]]\n| Best Drama Anthology\n| ''Magpakailanman''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Single Performance by an Actor\n| Jeremy Marquez (\"Pag-Ahon sa Lusak\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | Best Single Performance by an Actress\n| [[Alessandra de Rossi]] (\"Pag-Ahon sa Lusak\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Jean Garcia (\"Kalbaryo ng Isang Ina\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 2007\n| Catholic Mass Media Award\n| Best Drama Series/Program\n| rowspan=\"2\" | ''Magpakailanman''\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pep.ph/news/15305/Catholic-Mass-Media-Awards-bares-list-of-winners-for-2007|title=Catholic Mass Media Awards bares list of winners for 2007 - PEP.ph: The Number One Site for Philippine Showbiz|author=PEP.ph|date=30 October 2007|work=pep.ph}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | [[21st PMPC Star Awards for Television]] \n| Best Drama Anthology\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | Best Single Performance By An Actress\n| [[Gina Alajar]] (\"Liyab ng Pag-Asa\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Pauleen Luna]] (\"Sa Dulo ng Pag-Ibig: The Olivia Ortiz Story\")\n| {{won}}\n!\n|-\n| Lorna Tolentino (\"Hiram na Haplos\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2008\n| colspan=\"2\" | Anak TV Seal\n| rowspan=\"3\" | ''Magpakailanman''\n| {{won}}\n| <ref name=\"gmanewmedia,inc.\"/>\n|-\n| [[22nd PMPC Star Awards for Television]]\n| Best Drama Anthology\n| {{nom}}\n!\n|-\n| 2009\n| colspan=\"2\" | Anak TV Seal\n| {{won}}\n| <ref name=\"gmanewmedia,inc.\">{{cite web|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/entertainment/gma/articles/2012-11-09/8158/Magpakailanman-returns-to-Philippine-TV-this-November|title=Magpakailanman returns to Philippine TV this November|author=GMA New Media, Inc.|work=gmanetwork.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2013\n| Gawad