ision\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2015\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[29th PMPC Star Awards for Television]]\n| Best Drama Anthology\n| ''Magpakailanman''\n| {{Won}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" | <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rappler.com/entertainment/news/114712-winners-pmpc-star-awards-television-2015 |title= FULL LIST: Winners, 2015 PMPC Star Awards for TV |date=December 4, 2015 |accessdate=April 26, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Single Performance by an Actor\n| [[Mike Tan]] (\"8 Shades of Gay: The Tubato Family Story\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Single Performance by an Actress\n| Alessandra de Rossi (\"Sabit-sabit, Kabit-kabit, Mga Pusong Malupit\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2016\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[30th PMPC Star Awards for Television]]\n| Best Drama Anthology\n| ''Magpakailanman''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" | <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rappler.com/entertainment/news/150088-winners-pmpc-star-awards-2016-television|title=LIST: Winners, PMPC Star Awards 2016 \u2013 television|date=October 10, 2016|publisher=Rappler|access-date=April 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | Best Single Performance by an Actor\n| Kristofer Martin (\"Mag-Ama sa Bilangguan\")\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[John Arcilla]] (\"Mag-Ama sa Bilangguan\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2017\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[31st PMPC Star Awards for Television]]\n| Best Drama Anthology\n| ''Magpakailanman''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" | <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gmanetwork.com/entertainment/showbiznews/news/8183/in-photos-kapuso-winners-at-the-31st-pmpc-star-awards-for-television/photo |title=IN PHOTOS: Kapuso winners at the 31st PMPC Star Awards for Television |author=Soriano, Gia Allana |website=www.gmanetwork.com |accessdate=April 26, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Single Performance by an Actor\n| [[Rocco Nacino]] (\"Losing Jeffrey, Finding Jason\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Single Performance by an Actress\n| [[Janice de Belen]] (\"Ang Swerteng Hatid ng Pera sa Basura\")\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2018\n