41\u0442\u0430\u0444\u0430\u0435\u0432}}; born 7 September 1992) is a [[Russia]]n [[association football|football]] player.\n\n==Club career==\nHe made his debut in the [[Russian Second Division]] for [[FC Torpedo Armavir]] on 31 July 2013 in a game against [[FC MITOS Novocherkassk]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Russian Football Union]]|url=http://rfspro.ru/cgi-bin/player/script2.cgi?par1=117203|title=Career Summary|date=30 May 2013|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130908184530/http://rfspro.ru/cgi-bin/player/script2.cgi?par1=117203|archivedate=8 September 2013}}</ref>\n\nHe made his [[Russian Football National League]] debut for [[FC Fakel Voronezh]] on 12 March 2016 in a game against [[FC Tyumen]].\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://news.sportbox.ru/Vidy_sporta/Futbol/stats/man_1250352683 Career summary by sportbox.ru]\n* {{RPL player|Mustafaev-Bunyamudin}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mustafayev, Bunyamudin}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:People from Akhtynsky District]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Russian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:FC Chernomorets Novorossiysk players]]\n[[Category:FC Fakel Voronezh players]]\n[[Category:FC Armavir players]]\n[[Category:FC Kuban Krasnodar players]]\n\n{{Russia-footy-forward-1990s-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Zyxw", "label": "safe", "comment": "update sportbox.ru link", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bunyamudin_Mustafayev"}
